data.description: Beautiful Stone Creek home seeks long-term relationship!!!!!  If you like updated faucets, five-foot walk-in pantries, new LVP flooring, updated bathrooms, pullout trashcans and hampers, built-in dining nooks with storage, gorgeous lighting, and an amazing primary suite with dressing area, and private treelined view! Then get in touch!!   House also has new interior/exterior paint, steel garage cabinets and drawers, a large dog washing tub, and a guest room with desk area for your little hide away!  Closet systems, two large LG TVs (newer), one 32" TV, and two electric fireplaces!!!!!  Home has a washer/dryer combo, pedestal washer and a steam dryer.  Heat Pump was replaced with upgraded unit in August 2023.  The biggest appeal - the neighbors!  Truly the best!!  Kind, funny, non-intrusive, but great to share a meal with.  And there are many all around this home.  The home sits on a privacy lot, no one looking in on you, wonderful if you want to read a book enjoy a sip of morning coffee, or enjoy a glass of wine at the end of a fun filled day in Stone Creek.  The amenities are second to none and you are going to be simply amazed.  Home is priced without furniture, however it can be purchased furnished, please contact realtor for details.  Home inspection was done in July 2023 for your review.
